<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Zan lungkham um zana,
 I Lalpau Isu chun, &quot;Ziehi ka taksa leh,
 Ka thisan dawn ding chu,
 Nei hetzing nangun&quot; ti'n.

[V2]
 Hukdampa a deih puou,
 Zion kulhpi sung ah;
 A panpih a um puou,
 Thing hansedawl A bel,

[V3]
 2. &quot;Tho tiemu zie apat,
 Hin chieh dawk meng hitiu; Amah chu gilo in,
 Sim unau tih zik kha;
 Hung tung ding ahi tai&quot;.

[V4]
 3. Tichun a chieh dawk ui,
 Olivet tang lamah; Thiempu lalpente leh,
 Sepaih mawlh chaw i lawi chun;
 Amah kan in, khen uh.

[V5]
 4. Enghona lal puon leh,
 Linglukhuk mak tak tawh; Kalvari lam zuona,
 A chiehpih lai u khan ;
 Panpih ding A nei puoi.

[V6]
 5. Kalvari tangpi khu,
 Ni chengin ka thil a; Ka Hukdampa deihtak,
 Gilo kala ding khan;
 Ka thinlai a lun ie.</lyrics>
<title>Nei Hetzing Nangun</title>
<hymn_number>57</hymn_number>
<author>Taivela</author>
</song>